         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">29/6/83 ¶  ¶ I thought it best, dear Mr Wilson, to send the letter, concerning the £60.9/- ¶ M to G. Berry, 28 June 1883. ¶  ¶ before the end of the finance-year, and gave it to my Assistant, as he ha...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">83.06.29a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To Thomas Wilson</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Y83/6227, unit 1416, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence, VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">29/6/83</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I thought it best, dear Mr Wilson, to send the letter, concerning the £60.9/-<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>M to G. Berry, 28 June 1883.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>before the end of the finance-year, and gave it to my Assistant, as he had to go to your Accountant about the settlement of the £51.- .-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>for the iron-cases got from the penal department last year,<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to G. Berry, 28 June 1883 (in this edition as 83-06-28a).</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>the Treasury having a day or two ago sent back the papers.<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn2" n="3">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Papers not found.</p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Altho' you<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>kindly said<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>that there was time for some months for sundry additions to the Estimates, I have thought that perhaps, to simplify matters, the £60.9 might be recovered by adding the words "including arrears" after the item of £330.-<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>miscellaneous votes of Gov Botanist on the ordinary estimates for the coming year. Perhaps however that can not be done; but then at all events you have my letter, should a favorable opportunity arise to use it.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Regardfully your</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
